entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by for arrival of transport. Once it arrives, dock with the transport and make the trade.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Ok, looks like we are all set. Good luck.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Alright, we will make the trade. Stand by for the transfer of pelts for the chips.
entries.failed_destroyed: We needed those goods to trade to the Rendal Company in Corellia. Come on back and we will see if we can sort this out.
entries.found_loc_d: Alright, I have updated the meeting location of the Harkon transport. Trade him the pelts that are on your ship for the computer control chips.
entries.hello_d: You must be the new pilot. Go ahead and dock whenever you are ready. We will then make the cargo transfer.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the Rendal Company's ship and trade the pelt for the chips.
entries.quest_location_d: The Rendal Trading Company's ship, with the load of computer control chips, will meet you in the Naboo system.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: You shouldn't have any problems with this stage of the mission since you are not transferring anything illegal...yet.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_t: Meet the Rendal Trading Company's Ship
entries.split_quest_alert: Ok, now on to the next step. Head to Corellia and trade the computer chips to the Harkon for a load of blaster crystals for Nym's boys in Lok.
entries.title: Naboo System: Smuggling for the Trandoshans Part I
entries.title_d: Fezrik has hired you to run several tasks in order to get the Trandoshan slavers a load of glitterdust. Your first step is to trade some uller pelts that are in high demand on Naboo for a load of computer control chips.
